docs.title: Brainsmith - Coming Soon
docs.text:
Launch Date: November 2025

Brainsmith is an open-source compiler that automates the design and implementation of neural network accelerators on FPGAs. Stay tuned for our official release!

docs.title: About
docs.text: Brainsmith is developed through a collaboration between Microsoft and AMD, building upon industry-leading open-source frameworks FINN and QONNX with a focus on modularity, extensibility, and automation.
